      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s priced to move and could be a great fit for someone after cheap, straightforward motoring. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it has plenty of life left for the right buyer and would suit someone who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of tidying as they go. A sensible budget-friendly option for a first car, a spare runabout, or a handy project. If you want something affordable from a friendly seller who\u2019ll be upfront with you, this is well worth a look.",
